General.Name: Peppermint Innovation Ltd
General.Description: Peppermint Innovation Limited engages in the development and commercialization of mobile banking, payment, and remittance platform primarily in the Philippines. It operates Peppermint Platform, a white label mobile app banking platform and mobile app micro enterprise platform that offers payments, remittance, delivery and logistics, ecommerce, and financial services. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
